    quickml.supervised.classifier.downsamplingPredictiveModel
    A predictive model wrapper and related classes that can be used to improve performance on highly imbalanced datasets with two possible classifications (a majority classification and a minority classification).

  • Classes in quickml.supervised used by quickml.supervised 
    Class and Description
    PredictiveModel
    A predictive model, typically created by a supervised learning algorithm.
    PredictiveModelBuilder
    A supervised learning algorithm, which, given data, will generate a PredictiveModel.
    PredictiveModelBuilderBuilder
    Created by alexanderhawk on 3/4/14.
    PredictiveModelWithDataBuilder
    PredictiveModelBuilder that supports adding data to predictive models The builder will keep track of the number of times the model has been built, and if the rebuild threshold is passed the model will be rebuilt If the split node threshold is passed the leaves will be rebuilt
    UpdatablePredictiveModelBuilder
    Created by chrisreeves on 5/22/14.
